abstract: Saudi-backed Yemeni troops take full control of port of Aden from Shiite rebels.
lead_paragraph: Saudi-backed Yemeni troops took full control of Aden from Shiite rebels, and the airport reopened.

headline.main: Yemen: Rebels Ousted From a Port City, Officials Say
